Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,--------------------- OP ---------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.09,0:01:55.72,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,この瞳は 鮮やかに舞う
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.84,0:01:58.43,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君しかしらない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.64,0:02:02.02,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,踏み込んで 目覚める
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.68,0:02:07.23,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}セガイヘ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.02,0:02:13.28,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}うつむき過ぎて小さい
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.70,0:02:18.45,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}僕だけの景色が
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.91,0:02:25.46,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}組み立てたジオラマの嘘だと
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.58,0:02:31.17,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}合わせづらい視点に気づいている
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.59,0:02:41.51,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}駆け出してゆく未来は 美しさを手に
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.89,0:02:50.11,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}それぞれが飛べる場所を  問い掛けてく
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.74,0:02:56.45,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,この瞳は 鮮やかに舞う
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.53,0:02:59.28,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君しかしらない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.37,0:03:04.91,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加速して初めて行ける僕は 僕の先へ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.04,0:03:07.75,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,もっと高く　もっと強く
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.83,0:03:10.50,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君に届きたい
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.63,0:03:14.01,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,踏み込んで 目覚める
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.71,0:03:18.47,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}Chasin' the world
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.05,0:01:28.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.09,0:01:55.72,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那眼眸中生動的舞姿
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.84,0:01:58.43,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯有你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.64,0:02:02.02,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因闖入而覺醒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.68,0:02:07.23,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}闖入這個世界
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.02,0:02:13.28,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}低頭看到的小小世界
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.70,0:02:18.45,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}那是只屬於我的景色
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.91,0:02:25.46,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}組合起來的幻想畫都是浮雲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.58,0:02:31.17,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}只注意到匯聚的痛苦視點
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.59,0:02:41.51,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}奔跑突圍 未來會在你手中美麗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.89,0:02:50.11,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}向飛過的地方提出疑問
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.74,0:02:56.45,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那眼眸中生動的舞姿
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.53,0:02:59.28,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯有你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.37,0:03:04.91,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加速之後 第一次能邁向我的前方
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.04,0:03:07.75,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邁得更高 變得更強
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.83,0:03:10.50,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要到你身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.63,0:03:14.01,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因闖入而覺醒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.71,0:03:18.47,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}Chasin' the world
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,--------------------- OP ---------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,--------------------- ED ---------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.83,0:22:15.04,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We are tossed by the waves of pain and tears
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.16,0:22:18.74,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm tossed into the fray tossed by various fortune
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.02,0:22:22.49,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wake up your brain!Flashed in the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.77,0:22:25.07,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's a burst of sensation
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.14,0:22:31.23,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“谛め”がくれた 安楽沈滞の世界
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.59,0:22:37.51,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,いつからだっただろう？ふいに輝き始めた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.63,0:22:40.71,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,変わらずにいてと愿うこと-
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.85,0:22:44.42,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,変わりゆく时に生きる仆ら-
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.52,0:22:47.60,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本当の声を…言い得ぬ梦を…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.66,0:22:51.61,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君と繋がった空へ　响かせて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.58,0:22:55.88,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,もっと强く…この両手で
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.99,0:22:59.20,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涙全て振り払えたら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.28,0:23:02.47,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“今度こそは…”つぶやく今と
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.61,0:23:05.64,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伤さえも无駄にしない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.82,0:23:08.94,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,もっと早く…君のもとへ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.13,0:23:12.32,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,たとえ羽が千切れようとも
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.43,0:23:15.59,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歪む世界　走り抜けて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.69,0:23:18.85,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覚のその向こうへ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.98,0:23:24.36,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“真実”と　加速してく
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.83,0:22:15.04,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We are tossed by the waves of pain and tears
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.16,0:22:18.74,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm tossed into the fray tossed by various fortune
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.02,0:22:22.49,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wake up your brain!Flashed in the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.77,0:22:25.07,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's a burst of sensation
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.14,0:22:31.23,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「放棄」所帶給我的 安樂但停滯的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.59,0:22:37.51,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知從什麼時候開始  突然間開始變得閃耀
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.63,0:22:40.71,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祈望永恆不變的我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.85,0:22:44.42,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在不斷改變地世界生存的我們
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.52,0:22:47.60,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的心聲…無法說出夢想…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.66,0:22:51.61,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,響徹著 這與你相連的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.58,0:22:55.88,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果更用力地…用你的雙手
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.99,0:22:59.20,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幫我揮去所有的淚水的話
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.28,0:23:02.47,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我將永不放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.61,0:23:05.64,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算這些傷痕也不會讓它白費
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.82,0:23:08.94,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更快地 前往你的身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.13,0:23:12.32,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使這雙翅膀被撕裂
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.43,0:23:15.59,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要奔出 這扭曲的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.69,0:23:18.85,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向著我所感受到的彼方前進
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.98,0:23:24.36,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我的「真實」去加速
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,--------------------- ED ---------------------
